<br>
The Fire of Themiscrya then heads off to carry out her orders.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=elektraamazon>Elektra Amazon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Visitor</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#993300>(2/21/03 5:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=50>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/ddelektradd/images/smelek.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: New arrivals.</span><hr size=1> Elektra had grinned an almost wicked smile when she met Hippolyte's gaze.  But, the amazon did not speak a word.  Only nodded in respect.  She followed the others outside and listened intently to Hippolyte's orders.  Elektra was ready for a fight.  Why else would she be here?<br>
<br>
When Lysia spoke, Elektra eyed the amazon for a moment.  She had known of Lysia for many years.  And was impressed that the amazon had risen in ranks so quickly.  Her arms were folded in front of her as she listened.  <br>
<br>
Then as Lysia walked off, Elektra walked over to Hippolyte.  &quot;Ti kanete tu, Hippolyte?&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=hippolyte>Hippolyte</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Golden Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 783<br> <font color=#993300>(2/21/03 5:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm66.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1.topic&index=51>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://www.themiscrya.i-p.com/Hippwknife1ezboard.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Preparing for the attack</span><hr size=1> Hippolyte tilted her head and looked up at the warrior.  Her face showing a bit of curiosity.  &quot;Kalla, Elektra.  I am good.  What has brought you out of the dark corners of the world?&quot;<br>
<br>
Hippolyte had raised a brow and then walked over to her horse, quickly assessing her weapons.  Not looking the amazon in the eye...she waited for an answer. <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>

