&quot;But, I can fight...I know I can.&quot;  pleaded Kara again.  &quot;I want to be an amazon.&quot;<br>
<br>
Hippolyte sighed and glanced over at Cassandra, who was watching.  Cassandra walked up to the both of them.<br>
